{"article_id":"COYLfQk69SP3A7DA","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Google News and Google News search engine results appear to show a \" strong preference \" for media organizations","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that are on the left of the political spectrum ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"a new report finds .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"The report from the media technology group AllSides , out Tuesday , analyzed Google News ' homepage and search engine results from the news page over a two-week period","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"and determined","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that news outlets with a `` left '' bias were more often prominently displayed .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"But the study found no evidence","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Google had intentionally altered search results for the purpose","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"of \" suppressing voices of conservatives , \"","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"as President Donald Trump has previously stated .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Trump has previously claimed","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"that Google and other search engines are \" rigged \" against him .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"`` Google search results for 'Trump News ' shows only the viewing/reporting of Fake News Media , ''","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Trump tweeted Aug. 28 .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"The administration has said","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"the president was considering regulations against the tech giant .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Google search results for \" Trump News \" shows only the viewing/reporting of Fake News Media .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"In other words , they have it RIGGED , for me & others ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"so that almost all stories & news is BAD .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Fake CNN is prominent .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Republican/Conservative & Fair Media is shut out .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"Illegal ?","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"96 % of ....","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"August 28 , 2018","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"John Gable , CEO of AllSides and author of the study , said","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"the bias is the result of \" most news online and most news consumption online","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"( being ) from a left perspective . \"","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"AllSides specializes in identifying media bias for the purpose","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"of providing balanced perspectives .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"The group uses a media bias ratings","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"based on popular opinion","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"to rank media outlets as either left , right or center .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"\" If you look at where people get news online","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"and you rate it ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"most of it is coming from the left , \"","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Gable said .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"He said","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"Google search results come from what is largely a \" popularity algorithm , \"","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"meaning that viewpoints","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"more people have","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"are more likely to be highlighted .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"As a result , viewpoints","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"that are outside the majority","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"don ' t appear as high up in search results .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"In this sense ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Gable said ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Google 's algorithm is unintentionally biased toward more popular perspectives ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and those are the results","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"users see .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"the danger in this is that it can play into people 's preconceived notions .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"`` Right now , technology overly puts a spotlight on the most popular perspective , or the perspective","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that most fits you ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"and that cuts out other perspectives , ''","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"`` It reduces an individual ' s ability","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"to decide for themselves","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"or know the whole story . ''","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Gable said","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"going forward , Google has to decide what role it wants to play .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"\" If their role is just to reflect the internet ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"they ' re doing a fine job , ''","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"`` ... If they think","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"their job is to empower people to decide for themselves ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"they actually need to make a change .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"A Google spokesperson told","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that `` search is not used","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"to set a political agenda . ''","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"`` When users type queries into the Google Search bar ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"our goal is to make sure","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"they receive the most relevant answers in a matter of seconds , ''","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"the spokesperson said ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that Google does n't `` bias our results toward any political ideology . ''","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Google and other tech companies have come increasingly under fire for charges","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"that search engines results do not treat conservatives fairly .","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"In late September , the Wall Street Journal reported","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"that Google employees had debated altering search results","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"after Trump 's travel ban against predominantly Muslim countries went into effect in January 2017 .","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"Google CEO Sundar Pichai later met with Republican lawmakers","depth":4},{"id":83,"text":"to discuss those concerns .","depth":4},{"id":84,"text":"Pichai will also testify before the House Judiciary Committee about Google 's business practices after the November midterms elections .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":169,"left":161,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":110,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":94,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":87,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":86,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":89,"right":92,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":89,"left":3,"right":88,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":88,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":92,"left":6,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":90,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":95,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":105,"right":107,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":98,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":16,"right":103,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":99,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":17,"right":18,"